Flaws::section
  Determining Flaws::text
    After a character's ability scores, race and class has been determined, the player may opt to roll for up to two flaws. Before rolling, the player is allowed to ban 1 of the possible options. For every flaw a character has, they can choose an extra feat at first level.

    A character cannot roll the same flaw twice. There is no way to remove a flaw.
  
